{
  "stem": "833.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I recall my father coming home livid.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Overnight, the Austrian government annexed Bosnia and Herzegovina.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And my father really furiously said that means only more problems for us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "There will be always problems down there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They never can live together, because the one-- the Catholic and the Orthodox and the Islamic people, they never can live together.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They somehow-- he used to say the devil has put them there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And he was ranting.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And then, of course, he said, that we will have trouble.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And that's when the world war started.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "That's when the shots were fired against the crown president of Austria, Franz Ferdinand and his wife-- that two shots that-- of that-- that radical student, Mr.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Princip, who was just-- not a high schooler.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I think he was already in college-- who shot both of them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And that started the war, which in retrospect-- and even then-- now, we like to talk about that-- even then, was the most idiotic conflict that ever was.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "There was really no issue.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "There was the issue of land grabbing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "There was the issue of-- of the-- the weapons industry to make more money on all sides.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And if you-- I just gave a lecture last March, last year March.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And I read the list of the war declarations of that-- of that 19-- the year 1918.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "It was funny.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "It was laughable that every war-- everybody in the world declared war against everybody else, from-- from Central Europe to Western Europe to Eastern Europe to Japan.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It changed only during World War I.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "See, there is one thing which I also observed during World War II when I had my students in Manila, and the young people.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When something as cataclysmic happens as a war--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Where were we?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
